# @no-proxy

### User Endpoints
@baseUrl = http://localhost:8000/api/v1
@token = your_jwt_token_here
@msToken = your_microsoft_access_token_here
@userId = b9526d59-8660-4634-869f-52502b979a5a

### Register with Entra ID (Recommended)
# Flow: User logs in via Entra ID in frontend -> sends MS token here
# Returns: User profile + backend JWT token
POST {{baseUrl}}/users/register
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "ms_access_token": "{{msToken}}"
}

### ========== User Profile Management ==========

### Get Current User Profile (by ID)
GET {{baseUrl}}/users/me?user_id={{userId}}

### Update User Profile
PATCH {{baseUrl}}/users/me?user_id={{userId}}
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "full_name": "Alice Johnson Updated",
  "avatar_url": "https://api.dicebear.com/7.x/avataaars/svg?seed=Alice"
}

### Update Bob's Profile with Avatar
PATCH {{baseUrl}}/users/me?user_id={{userId}}
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "full_name": "Bob Smith",
  "avatar_url": "https://api.dicebear.com/7.x/avataaars/svg?seed=Bob"
}

